  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>Last updated: June 18, 2025</p>

  <p>
    Welcome to <strong>MyLabs Accounts by RekietaLabs</strong>. Your privacy is important to us.
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our services.
  </p>

  <h2>1. What Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect the following types of information when you use MyLabs:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> A randomly generated UUID to identify your account within our system.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use MyLabs, including login activity, pages visited, and interactions.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Technical data such as your browser type, operating system, IP address, and device type.</li>
    <li><strong>Optional Profile Data:</strong> Any additional information you choose to provide (e.g., display name or email if applicable).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>We use your information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide and maintain your MyLabs account</li>
    <li>Track your progress and activity within our platform</li>
    <li>Improve the performance and usability of MyLabs</li>
    <li>Respond to inquiries and support requests</li>
    <li>Ensure the security of our services</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. How We Share Information</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not sell</strong> your personal information. We may share your data in the following cases:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>With trusted service providers who help us operate our platform (e.g., Appwrite for authentication and database storage)</li>
    <li>If required by law, legal process, or to protect our rights</li>
    <li>In connection with a business transfer, such as a merger or acquisition</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access, update, or delete your personal data</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent where processing is based on consent</li>
    <li>Request a copy of the data we hold about you</li>
  </ul>
  <p>If you'd like to exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <strong>support@rekietalabs.com</strong>.</p>

  <h2>5. How We Protect Your Data</h2>
  <p>We use industry-standard security measures, including encryption and access controls, to protect your personal data. However, no system is 100% secure, so we encourage you to protect your credentials and log out after each session.</p>

  <h2>6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>MyLabs is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If we learn we’ve collected information from a child under 13, we will delete it promptly.</p>

  <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Last updated" date at the top of the policy. We encourage you to review this policy regularly to stay informed about how we are protecting your data.</p>

  <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@rekietalabs.com</p>
  <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://rekietalabs.com">https://rekietalabs.com</a></p>

